*Verujemo* da će se situacija uskoro promeniti. (We believe that the situation will soon change.)

Čovek je *verovao* da će se njegov život promeniti. (The man believed that his life would change.)

*Verujem* da ćeš početi da se baviš sportom. (I believe that you will start doing sports.)

Svi *veruju* da je ona uspešna i da ima dobar posao. (Everyone believes that she is successful and has a good job.)

Jedino što *verujemo* je da će sve biti u redu. (The only thing we believe is that everything will be alright.)